title: NDFD, NOAA, Significant Wave Height in GOM coastal waters, USA, July 7, 2010
name: NDFD, NOAA, Significant Wave Height in GOM coastal waters, USA, July 7, 2010
description:
The poly shapefile shows significant wave height data for portions of coastal waters in the GOM.
The data was extracted from NDFD's extraction program and then converted to shapefile. 
Look elsewhere on Finder! for wave data over the next several days. Use key word "Wave height".
